OL,5, The money schools get from the         
OL,6, Department of Education to provide free
OL,7, period products has been cut by more   
OL,8, than 40%.                              
OL,10,FThe department said that the fall was  
OL,11,F"due to a combination of budget        
OL,12,Freductions and the level of need being 
OL,13,Flower than expected in 2022-23".       
OL,15,FThe annual funding for education was   
OL,16,Fcut in the recent budget from Northern 
OL,17,FIreland Secretary Chris Heaton-Harris. 
OL,19,FSome schemes aimed at disadvantaged    
OL,20,Fpupils have been stopped to save money.
